snippet.title: Kaiju-Oh Godzilla (Playthrough Pt. 1/5) - Wikizilla
snippet.description:
Playthrough part one of Kaiju-Oh Godzilla, the second biggest compilation of Toho monsters ever. This game was only released in Japan for the Gameboy, which is sad as this game is quite a bit of fun, but very and long challenging as well. This game can only be finished in one long sitting, as there are no passwords, cheat codes, or anything.
